{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4bd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2296a–3"},"text":"§ 2296a–3.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this part:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4be-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The term “active uranium or thorium processing site” means—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4bf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" any uranium or thorium processing site, including the mill, containing byproduct material for which a license (issued by the Nuclear Regulatory Commission or its predecessor agency under the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2011"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2011","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], or by a State as permitted under section 274 of such Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2021"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2021","children":[],"tail":")) for the production at such site of any uranium or thorium derived from ore—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" was in effect on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1978","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" was issued or renewed after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1978","children":[],"tail":"; or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/A/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" for which an application for renewal or issuance was pending on, or after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1978","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" any other real property or improvement on such real property that is determined by the Secretary or by a State as permitted under section 274 of the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2021"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2021","children":[],"tail":") to be—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in the vicinity of such site; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/1/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" contaminated with residual byproduct material;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “byproduct material” has the meaning given such term in section 11 e. (2) of the Atomic Energy Act of 1954,","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn003284"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn003284"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. The comma probably should not appear."}],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2014/e/2"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2014(e)(2)","children":[],"tail":"); and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s2296a–3/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “decontamination, decommissioning, reclamation, and other remedial action” means work performed prior to or subsequent to ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"October 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", which is necessary to comply with all applicable requirements of the Uranium Mill Tailings Radiation Control Act of 1978 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s7901"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 7901","children":[],"tail":" et seq.), or where appropriate, with requirements established by a State that is a party to a discontinuance agreement under section 274 of the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2021"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2021","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbc17a4c8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/486/tX/s1004"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–486, title X, § 1004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-24"},"text":"Oct. 24, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/2947"},"text":"106 Stat. 2947","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbc17a4c9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbc17a4ca-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbc17a4cb-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Atomic Energy Act of 1954, referred to in par. (1)(A), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1946-08-01/ch724"},"text":"act Aug. 1, 1946, ch. 724","children":[],"tail":", as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1954-08-30/ch1073/s1"},"text":"act Aug. 30, 1954, ch. 1073, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/68/919"},"text":"68 Stat. 919","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter (§ 2011 et seq.). For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2011"},"text":"section 2011 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Uranium Mill Tailings Radiation Control Act of 1978, referred to in par. (3), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/604"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–604","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-11-08"},"text":"Nov. 8, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/3021"},"text":"92 Stat. 3021","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 88 (§ 7901 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s7901"},"text":"section 7901 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbc17a4cc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Energy Policy Act of 1992, and not as part of the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
